Be it ordained by the Council of the City of Cleveland:
Section 1. That the Use District of lands bounded and described as follows:
Beginning at the intersection of West 6th Street and St. Clair Avenue;
Thence easterly along the centerline of St. Clair Avenue to its intersection with the centerline of West 3rd Street;
Thence southerly along said centerline to its intersection with the centerline of Superior Avenue;
Thence westerly along said centerline to its intersection with the centerline of West 6th Street;
Thence northerly along said centerline to the place of origin;
